<p><span class="anchor" id="p33"></span><span class="c2">(٠٠٠ - ١٣٩٨ هـ- ٠٠٠ - ١٩٧٨ م)</span><a href="#p33" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
