<p><span class="anchor" id="p35"></span>توفي في ١٢ آذار <span class="c2">(مارس)</span> <span class="c2">(٥)</span>.<a href="#p35" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
